       - Complete migration strategy
       - Memory layout diagrams
       - Benefits and risk mitigations
       - Testing strategy
    
    **Testing:**
    âœ… System boots without bootloop
    âœ… PMM initializes correctly
    âœ… Kernel heap allocates 16MB
    âœ… Classic MM successfully allocates 2MB system + 6MB app heaps
    âœ… All Mac APIs (NewPtr, NewHandle) work via nanokernel backend
    
