       - PixelTrue bit extraction â†’ MacPaint_PixelTrue()
       - SetPixel/ClearPixel operations â†’ C bit manipulation
       - Buffer operations (Invert, Zero) â†’ C memset/XOR
       - Pattern expansion â†’ MacPaint_ExpandPattern()
    
    4. Pascal Main Program (MacPaint.p)
       - PROCEDURE/FUNCTION declarations â†’ C functions
       - VAR declarations â†’ static globals/locals
       - TYPE records â†’ C structs
       - Event loop â†’ System 7.1 Event Manager
    
